    "created_at": "2019-03-06T03:10:19Z",
    "updated_at": "2019-03-06T03:10:19Z",
    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "This is indeed a kind of a race specific to the poll-cv engine. This is happening because we are reusing an fd, specifically 3, for the proxy server. \r\nThe case that I am seeing is - we get a hangup on an fd and close the fd. We then open a new fd which gets the same fd number. poll-cv internally uses polling threads to poll over fds, and the result from the previous fd is being reused for the new fd, resulting in us seeing hangups on the new fds."
  },
